node.text: Have Pillsbury Crescent rolls in the fridge? Then we have 5 creative ways for you to enjoy them. From pineapple cheesecake bars to baked crescent churros, these recipes not only provide a tasty snack for the family, but also a little baking entertainment.

node.title: 5 Genius Ways to Use a Can of Crescent Dough

node.text: Let the little ones in on the holiday baking fun! These 5 Christmas cookies require kids' expertise on decorating! We can assure you that the whole family will have a jolly good time. 🎅 You can find the recipes by searching on Pillsbury.com!

node.title: 5 Christmas Cookies to Make with Kids
